text.section:
A return shall state, for the period that the return covers:
for a vendor making a retail sale in the State:
the gross proceeds of the business of the vendor;
the taxable price of sales on which the sales and use tax is computed; and
the sales and use tax due; and
for a vendor making a sale for use:
the total value of the tangible personal property or taxable service the use of which became subject to the sales and use tax; and
the sales and use tax due.
